<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ title }} | Blog Newscale</title>
  {% if description %}<meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">{% endif %}

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --verde-escuro: #14373C;
      --verde-medio: #435D51;
      --bege-claro: #D0D0CA;
      --marrom-areia: #B06E4A;
      --branco-fundo: #FBFBF9;
      --branco-puro: #FFFFFF;
      --font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font-family);
      background-color: var(--branco-fundo);
      color: #333;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      padding: 20px 0;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo img { height: 70px; width: auto; }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 30px; align-items: center; }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--verde-medio);
      font-weight: 500;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover, nav a.active {
      color: var(--marrom-areia);
      border-bottom-color: var(--marrom-areia);
    }
    .cta-nav {
      background-color: var(--marrom-areia);
      color: white !important;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      border-bottom: none !important;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease !important;
    }
    .cta-nav:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(176,110,74,0.4);
    }

    /* Post hero */
    .post-hero {
      background-color: var(--verde-escuro);
      padding: 70px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .post-hero .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .post-hero .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      color: var(--bege-claro);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .post-hero .back-link:hover { opacity: 1; }
    .post-meta {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--bege-claro);
      opacity: 0.75;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .post-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--branco-puro);
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .post-hero .lead {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--bege-claro);
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* Cover image */
    .cover-wrapper {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: -30px auto 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    .cover-wrapper img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      max-height: 480px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* Article body */
    .post-body {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 740px;
      margin: 60px auto 80px;
    }

    /* Prose styles para o conteúdo Markdown */
    .prose { color: #2d2d2d; }
    .prose h2 {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--verde-escuro);
      margin: 2.5em 0 0.8em;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .prose h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--verde-escuro);
      margin: 2em 0 0.6em;
    }
    .prose h4 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--verde-medio);
      margin: 1.5em 0 0.4em;
    }
    .prose p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 1.4em;
      color: #3a3a3a;
    }
    .prose strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--verde-escuro); }
    .prose em { font-style: italic; }
    .prose a {
      color: var(--marrom-areia);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .prose a:hover { opacity: 0.75; }
    .prose ul, .prose ol {
      margin: 1.2em 0 1.4em 1.5em;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }
    .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.4em; }
    .prose blockquote {
      border-left: 4px solid var(--marrom-areia);
      padding: 1em 1.5em;
      margin: 2em 0;
      background: rgba(176,110,74,0.06);
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--verde-medio);
    }
    .prose blockquote p { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .prose hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--bege-claro);
      margin: 2.5em 0;
    }
    .prose img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 1.5em 0;
    }
    .prose code {
      background: #f0f0ed;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .prose pre {
      background: var(--verde-escuro);
      color: var(--bege-claro);
      padding: 1.2em 1.5em;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 1.5em 0;
    }
    .prose pre code { background: none; padding: 0; }

    /* CTA pós-artigo */
    .post-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-escuro), var(--verde-medio));
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 60px 0 20px;
    }
    .post-cta h3 {
      color: var(--branco-puro);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .post-cta p {
      color: var(--bege-claro);
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .post-cta a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--marrom-areia);
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .post-cta a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(176,110,74,0.4);
    }

    /* Bottom back link */
    .bottom-back {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
    .bottom-back a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      color: var(--verde-medio);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .bottom-back a:hover { color: var(--marrom-areia); }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--verde-medio);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--bege-claro);
    }

    /* Responsivo */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
      nav { gap: 18px; }
      .post-cta { padding: 36px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="/"><img src="/LOGO 05@3x.png" alt="Newscale Consulting"></a>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Início</a>
      <a href="/quem-somos.html">Quem Somos</a>
      <a href="/blog/" class="active">Blog</a>
      <a href="/contato.html">Contato</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/5511963232908?text=Quero%20um%20diagn%C3%B3stico%20gratuito%20para%20meu%20neg%C3%B3cio" target="_blank" class="cta-nav">Diagnóstico Grátis</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="post-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/blog/" class="back-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
        Voltar ao Blog
      </a>
      <p class="post-meta">{{ date | ptDate }}</p>
      <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
      {% if description %}<p class="lead">{{ description }}</p>{% endif %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {% if cover %}
  <div class="cover-wrapper">
    <img src="{{ cover }}" alt="{{ title }}">
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="post-body">
    <article class="prose">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </article>

    <div class="post-cta">
      <h3>Pronto para automatizar seu negócio?</h3>
      <p>Descubra como a IA pode trabalhar por você 24 horas por dia — comece com um diagnóstico gratuito.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/5511963232908?text=Quero%20um%20diagn%C3%B3stico%20gratuito%20para%20meu%20neg%C3%B3cio" target="_blank">Falar com a Newscale</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-back">
      <a href="/blog/">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
        Ver todos os artigos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Newscale. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
